nodes.text: Eldr'har was a female Stereb who lived on Prakith during the time of the Galactic Empire.

Eldr'har was the leader of a group of Stereb who lived underground near to Prak City. When a group of Alderaanian Resistance agents traveled to Prakith, they rescued the missing Stereb Herdr'tui and brought him back to Eldr'har's community. She was very pleased by this and thanked the agents.
